      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A microbiology study is examining the transformation of non-toxigenic Corynebacterium diphtheriae into a toxigenic form through bacteriophage interaction. What genetic transfer method is involved in this conversion?</span></span></span></span></p>",
