          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">To enable bacteria to resist viral infections through sequence-specific DNA cleavage</span></span></span></span></p>"
